<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://static.independent.co.uk/s3fs-public/thumbnails/image/2018/05/22/13/gin-cocktails.jpg?w968h681);">
